      <li><strong>GP visit (private):</strong> $80-150</li>
      <li><strong>Specialist consultation:</strong> $150-300</li>
      <li><strong>Emergency room:</strong> $200-500</li>
      <li><strong>Hospital stay per day:</strong> $500-1,200</li>
    </ul>
